{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-jsx","path":"/check-if-a-string-contains-substring-in-python","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"string-code-classlanguage-textcontainscode-method-in-python\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#string-code-classlanguage-textcontainscode-method-in-python\" aria-label=\"string code classlanguage textcontainscode method in python permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>String <code class=\"language-text\">contains</code> method in Python</h1>\n<p>Python's alternative to <code class=\"language-text\">String.contains</code> is the keyword <code class=\"language-text\">in</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">foobar <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'foobar'</span>\nsubstr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'foo'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> substr <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> foobar<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Yes'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">else</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'No'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Prints 'Yes'</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Although under the hood Python may use some of the <a href=\"https://docs.python.org/3/reference/datamodel.html#special-method-names\">magic methods</a> like\n<a href=\"https://docs.python.org/3/reference/datamodel.html#object.__contains__\"><code class=\"language-text\">__contains__</code></a>, <code class=\"language-text\">__iter__</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">__getitem__</code>, you should try to avoid using\nthese methods directly on strings. These are useful when defining your own type\nwith testing membership capabilities.</p>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"String  method in Python Python's alternative to  is the keyword . Although under the hood Python may use some of the magic methods like…","frontmatter":{"title":"Check if a string contains substring in Python","date":"2020-05-27 10:03:50 +0200","categories":["python"],"tags":["string","contains","python","python3"],"description":null,"keywords":"string, contains, python, python3","author":"Pavle Jonoski","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":204,"height":132,"src":"/static/c4fa3c5851be4bf4f2f39daf2e691d3b/02521/python.png","srcSet":"/static/c4fa3c5851be4bf4f2f39daf2e691d3b/02521/python.png 1x"}}}},"fields":{"slug":"/check-if-a-string-contains-substring-in-python","date":"2020-05-27T08:03:50.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/check-if-a-string-contains-substring-in-python","nexttitle":"NotImplemented vs NotImplementedError in Python","nextslug":"/notimplemented-vs-notimplementederror-in-python","prevtitle":"Java String.equals vs '=='","prevslug":"/java-stringequals-vs","tagList":["java","interface","callbacks","asynchronus calls","python","pandas","abstraction","OOP","Class","collection","API","Map","HashMap","LinkedHashMap","TreeMap","Python","cli","args","argparse","javascript","es6","beginner","codenewbie","Primary_key","implementation","Composite